Faust-Witkowsky  vorgelesen;
         An edition of Goethe's Faust, made by Georg Witkowski, published in 1906. From other diary entries that mention Witkowski (see especially July 4 and 6), it is likely that Schenker started with the editor's introduction.
         außerdem lese ich Tacitus’ Annalen u. Platons Phaedon.

Von Dahms (Br.= OJ 10/1, [96]): dankt für das Jahrbuch, wird darüber in Schwers Zeitung, Berlin, schreiben;
         Dahms's review appeared in the Allgemeine Musikzeitung on December 24, 1926. (A review by Dahms of Meisterwerk 2 appeared in the same journal on February 3, 1928. Both are preserved in Schenker's scrapbook (OC 2).)
         – reist anfangs August nach Berlin, um den Almanach in Bewegung zu setzen.
